WEBVTT

00:00:02.121 --> 00:00:04.072
Helman, ZE KEN, BESEDER.

00:00:04.062 --> 00:00:08.393
iz ir zent ongekum- hot zi zi eynen arayngenumen tsu,

00:00:06.913 --> 00:00:10.302
host zi mikh genumen tsu zikh aroyf. zi iz di,

00:00:10.302 --> 00:00:13.795
zi zi hot nisht gehat keyn man, zi iz geven an almone,

00:00:13.795 --> 00:00:16.712
un zi hot gehat a p- di k- kinder.

00:00:16.853 --> 00:00:19.192
sheyn vi di lyalkes!

00:00:19.738 --> 00:00:21.402
MALKAT HAYOFI!

00:00:21.493 --> 00:00:23.861
un zey hobn gehat benkartn fun di

00:00:23.861 --> 00:00:25.827
eygntimer fun dem git,

00:00:25.827 --> 00:00:31.387
a git heyst a farmegn, a groysn, un zey hobn parobkes azelkhes vos arbetn.

00:00:31.387 --> 00:00:35.645
ikh hob nisht gezen dortn keyn balbatim. ikh hob gezen nor di parobkes.

00:00:35.820 --> 00:00:40.876
ikh kum aroyf azoy tsunoyf geklapt fun di breter azelkhe mine, ale shlofn tsuzamen.

00:00:41.001 --> 00:00:43.492
ikh hob mikh oykh geleygt. zi hot mikh aroyfgenumen un,

00:00:43.617 --> 00:00:46.226
un ikh bin geblibn dortn. hot men ongehoybn redn,

00:00:46.603 --> 00:00:48.414
hobn zey mikh ongenumen, ikh

00:00:48.414 --> 00:00:53.330
az a poylishe nisht, ikh hob nisht oysgezen UNK. dernokh hot zi mir gezogt az m'hot azoy geredt,

00:00:53.505 --> 00:00:56.750
z- zo- ikh hob gemeynt bist a frantsuske.

00:00:56.750 --> 00:00:58.497
hob ikh ir dertseylt azoy.

00:00:58.497 --> 00:01:00.958
her, mayn man iz geven an ofitsir,

00:01:01.403 --> 00:01:03.169
un im genumen di armey,

00:01:03.546 --> 00:01:07.809
un dakht zikh mir az er lebt nisht, vayl m'hot ale ofitsirn heyst araynge-

00:01:08.878 --> 00:01:10.998
v- barn militer.

00:01:11.562 --> 00:01:13.328
un ikh hob, zog ikh, a kind,

00:01:13.384 --> 00:01:20.010
hob ikh zi iberge- hob ikh in Prage. ikh hob ir gezogt di vorheyt, in Prage, in dos iz nokh unter Prage geven vu zi iz geven.

00:01:20.387 --> 00:01:27.477
un ikh darf, un ven s'hot zikh ongehoybn e- endikn dos di milkhome, zey ho- zey hobn ongehoybn shoyn antloyfn di daytshn,

00:01:27.522 --> 00:01:31.363
zenen aroysgegangen fun di stodoles vu zey UNK, a stodole heyst

00:01:31.429 --> 00:01:36.809
a a sha- a a a a a plats vu m- zey haltn alding

00:01:36.809 --> 00:01:41.945
shtroy, di hober, alding, heyst a stodole.

00:01:41.945 --> 00:01:44.931
hobn UNK gelegn bahaltn shoyn daytshn,

00:01:44.931 --> 00:01:48.140
vayl di s'zenen ongekumen di bolshevikes shoyn nokh der Vaysl,

00:01:48.771 --> 00:01:51.600
un azoy vi ikh hob doser gezen,

00:01:51.775 --> 00:01:54.733
hob ikh ir, hob ikh mikh gegebn a pak ayn,

00:01:54.733 --> 00:01:59.880
ikh hob epes gehat fun lang ongegreyt a por shikhelekh, m'hot dokh gevust s'vet zikh endikn. un m'hot gevust

00:01:59.880 --> 00:02:09.785
az iz di di di bolshevikes shteyen in yener zayt Vaysl, zey viln ekstere az di polyakn zoln zikh aleyn oysblut- oys blutikn,

00:02:09.785 --> 00:02:15.090
un dernokhn veln zey k- vet zey onkumen laykhter dos geyn forverts. un oyf Berlin.

00:02:15.197 --> 00:02:21.721
un azoy iz gevezn, in yanuar, mer oder veyniker,

00:02:21.897 --> 00:02:26.925
dem akhtsetn oder in fift- zibetsetn oder in akhtsetn, ikh gedenk nisht genoy. alnfals,

00:02:27.000 --> 00:02:29.375
azoy vi zey zenen ongekumen tsu undz,

00:02:29.375 --> 00:02:32.500
un di daytshn ongehoybn aroysgeyn fun di stodoles,

00:02:32.500 --> 00:02:35.550
un zey hobn aroysgenumen vayse tikhlekh, un eyner hot gekhapt

00:02:35.550 --> 00:02:41.025
fotografyes gevizn un er hot, un zey hobn geveynt vi di kleyne kinder, di o- di di,

00:02:39.328 --> 00:02:41.296
far vos fotografyes?

00:02:41.197 --> 00:02:43.122
fun di mishpokhes zeyere.

00:02:41.708 --> 00:02:45.009
fun di mishpokhe. m'zol hobn rakhmones oyf zey.

00:02:43.530 --> 00:02:47.155
m'zol hobn rakhmones, mit di vay- mit vayse doser.

00:02:47.155 --> 00:02:49.751
hob ikh shoyn gepakt a plet-zak,

00:02:49.808 --> 00:02:56.721
mit alts vos ikh hob gehat, ikh hob epes gehat epes gekoyft in Byale oykhet, in KOSCIOL bin ikh dort oykh geganen.

00:02:56.811 --> 00:02:58.138
un,

00:02:57.368 --> 00:03:03.251
dort ven ir zent geven mit zey, mit di polyakn, ze- zent ir geven als kristin?

00:03:00.220 --> 00:03:03.081
yo, hob ikh dokh gemuzt fa-

00:03:03.113 --> 00:03:07.458
als als kristin. zey iz nisht ayngefaln. zey hobn zikh gekent zikh be-

00:03:07.458 --> 00:03:10.638
azelkhe vos hobn gearbet yetst in dem git,

00:03:10.638 --> 00:03:12.523
zey hobn dokh nisht gehat gornisht keyn eygntum.

00:03:12.594 --> 00:03:17.746
nor zey hobn gekrign esn tsugeteylt dortn un efsher a a por zlotes.

00:03:18.040 --> 00:03:21.729
ober zi iz geven an almone, zi hot nisht gehat keyn man, nor a zun hot zi gehat.

00:03:22.798 --> 00:03:26.119
hot z- iz far vos hob ikh ir dertseylt az ikh hob a man?

00:03:26.119 --> 00:03:29.711
vayl zi hot mir gegebn ontsugehern, zi vil ikh zol khasene hobn mit dem zun.

00:03:30.375 --> 00:03:33.052
un ikh volt geven khasene gehat, ven ikh ken mikh

00:03:33.058 --> 00:03:42.564
z- oyszogn farn farn shto- farn heylikn, farn galekh, vayl s- un sh- un dos bin ikh gegangen, vayl ale zenen geganen.

00:03:42.564 --> 00:03:45.838
di Varshever vos zenen geven, di polyakn, hobn oysgezen,

00:03:45.838 --> 00:03:50.934
ikh hob zey geneyt fun kotsn ontsutun, a hitl fun, a kots veystu vos s'heyst?

00:03:50.934 --> 00:03:55.246
aza min, nisht vi azoy, a sheyne, an elegante, azoy vi farn militer.

00:03:51.013 --> 00:03:52.340
a deke.

00:03:55.246 --> 00:03:58.855
fun fun alding, hob ikh tsum ersht geneyt in der hant,

00:03:59.586 --> 00:04:01.031
zey hobn mir batsolt.

00:04:01.645 --> 00:04:04.896
dernokhn hob ikh ir, ikh hob shoyn gezen ikh hob a por funt,

00:04:05.020 --> 00:04:10.197
z- hob ikh zey gezogt, forts ergets tsu, vu iz amnentstn? hobn zey gezogt keyn Bolonye.

00:04:10.197 --> 00:04:14.542
hob ikh gekoyft far zey tsvey kleyne yetst-geboyrene khazeyrimlekh,

00:04:14.542 --> 00:04:16.719
zey hobn zikh dos unter gepashet.

00:04:16.719 --> 00:04:22.833
iz shoyn geven a bisl milkh, hot zi shoyn gekokht oyf milkh a bisl ZUREK hot es geheysn.

00:04:22.992 --> 00:04:27.171
der ZUREK hot gehat ale taymim bay mir, ikh hob ongehoybn oyszen azoy o.

00:04:27.987 --> 00:04:30.951
un di zey zenen opgetretn in gantsn.

00:04:31.092 --> 00:04:37.110
di di uzbekn, oyf tsurik oyf oyf oyf Berlin.

00:04:36.947 --> 00:04:39.624
vi lang zent ir geven dort bay zey?

00:04:39.377 --> 00:04:41.699
bay zey bin ikh gevezn

00:04:42.516 --> 00:04:46.864
fun poylishn oyfshtand, ven m'iz aroys, heyst a gantsn vinter.

00:04:46.988 --> 00:04:54.730
JESIEN JESIEN un un di un vinter. yo, dos heyst fun fir un fertsikstn biz in finf un fertsikstn yanuar.

00:04:49.654 --> 00:04:51.386
herbst un vinter.

00:04:54.730 --> 00:04:56.179
onheyb yanuar.

00:04:56.168 --> 00:04:58.035
un demolts hot ir zikh a-

00:04:56.353 --> 00:04:58.215
ze'mir shoyn geven fray.

00:04:58.215 --> 00:05:00.991
demolts hob ikh shoyn genumen ayngepakt a pekl,

00:05:00.991 --> 00:05:07.327
un a por shikhelekh hob ikh gehat fun lang ongegreyt, gekoyft oyf tsvelef k- kilometer fun zey,

00:05:07.336 --> 00:05:09.926
iz geven a mark, in Bloyne,

00:05:09.926 --> 00:05:14.385
un dortn take, Bloyne, iz der Zigmund dershosn gevorn.

00:05:14.507 --> 00:05:19.860
un a- barn Bund az m'geyt oyf a, un zey makhn akademyes in akhtstn tog fun oyfshtand,

00:05:19.900 --> 00:05:24.480
hobn zey gezogt er iz umgeku- un er shraybt oykhet do, der Bernard, der firer fun Bund,

00:05:24.480 --> 00:05:26.780
az er iz um- umgekumen in oyfshtand. neyn.

00:05:26.780 --> 00:05:30.000
er iz geven keseyder oyf der arisher zayt un tsugeshtelt gever.

00:05:30.593 --> 00:05:34.633
un dershosn gevorn iz er als yid. m'hot im derkent epes ver

00:05:34.633 --> 00:05:37.393
in Bloyne take un dort iz er dershosn gevorn.

00:05:37.393 --> 00:05:40.193
dos hob ikh gehert fun dakh fun di arbetorers,

00:05:41.173 --> 00:05:42.989
vos zey hobn geredt di politik.

00:05:49.054 --> 00:05:54.396
ikh hob im ayngepakt, ikh hob ikh hob zikh azoy vi zey zenen geshtanen zikh gebetn er zol zey rateven,

00:05:54.396 --> 00:05:56.556
di daytshn vos hobn nisht bavizn

00:05:56.556 --> 00:05:59.316
zikh tsu tsu tsu tsu antloyfn.

00:05:59.420 --> 00:06:01.994
hobn hobn di rusn genumen.

00:06:01.994 --> 00:06:08.842
un ikh bin aroys oyfn veg, tsu fus mit a plet-zak,

00:06:09.355 --> 00:06:13.730
un epes a keyshl oykhet dakht zikh, tsi nisht keyn ke- yo, ikh hob gehat a keyshl

00:06:13.730 --> 00:06:19.257
epes oykhet, vayl ikh hob gehat a por shikhlekh un nokh epes, ikh veys nisht vos, farn kind tsugegreyt.

00:06:19.257 --> 00:06:20.734
dem gantsn vinter

00:06:20.734 --> 00:06:25.460
hob ikh un dem herbst, vifl ikh hob fardint, hob ikh zey gegebn di proshakes,

00:06:25.516 --> 00:06:28.096
un ikh hob zey gegebn yedes mol a por zlotes,

00:06:28.096 --> 00:06:31.616
un ikh ikh hob dokh fardint fun dem vos ikh hob gearbet

00:06:31.616 --> 00:06:34.596
far di Varshever, far di opgebrenter, polyakn,

00:06:34.596 --> 00:06:37.836
fun di kotsn, vos emetser hot gehat, vos er hot gebrengt.

00:06:37.975 --> 00:06:40.938
un s'gevezn in nay yor,

00:06:41.333 --> 00:06:44.803
iz arayngekumen, hob ikh nisht gevust vos m'tut

00:06:45.282 --> 00:06:49.421
mit dem mit di OPLATKIS, iz gekumen der der galekh,

00:06:49.421 --> 00:06:54.168
ober er hot gevust, ikh hob gezen in di oygn az er derkent az ikh bin a yidishe.

00:06:54.394 --> 00:06:56.669
vayl ikh hob nisht ge-

00:06:54.748 --> 00:06:57.746
er hot zikh nisht oyfge- er hot zikh, er hot gornisht gezogt?

00:06:56.669 --> 00:06:59.636
neyn. er hot gornisht gezogt.

00:06:59.693 --> 00:07:04.445
er hot nor gezen tsi ikh tu epes. yakh hob nisht gevust az m'darf aropshlingen

00:07:04.485 --> 00:07:07.938
di OPLATKIS vos m'get. ikh hob nisht gevust di gezetsn.

00:07:07.590 --> 00:07:10.385
in di tume, in di k- in di kirkhe.

00:07:10.476 --> 00:07:14.109
nisht in di kirkhe, in shtub. in yedn shtub kumt er on vuntshn,

00:07:13.918 --> 00:07:14.975
yo?

00:07:14.109 --> 00:07:18.099
un in Varshe iz nisht azoy, in Varshe iz er nisht efsher geven.

00:07:18.099 --> 00:07:21.919
nor in do a kleyne plats un do iz der der KOSCIOL oykhet do,

00:07:21.919 --> 00:07:24.559
un s'do der reyner dos, iz er geganen in di khalupes arayn,

00:07:24.559 --> 00:07:27.559
in di shtubn arayn, shtubn, s'geven khalupes azelkhe.

00:07:27.584 --> 00:07:30.129
azoy vi sukes gemakhte.

00:07:30.405 --> 00:07:31.940
iz er gekumen,

00:07:32.080 --> 00:07:38.940
iz men gezesn oyf dem bet vu m'geshlofn, s'geven breter tsunoyf geklapt azoy, firkantike shtiker breter, un ale hobn zikh

00:07:38.940 --> 00:07:42.780
oysgetsoygn m'geshlofn. shreklekh oreme mentshn gevezn.

00:07:43.787 --> 00:07:50.919
un er un nemt er un tsebrekht er tsu aza pletsele tsebrekht er, un get yedn eynem in moyl arayn.

00:07:51.229 --> 00:07:53.602
un ikh hob nisht gevust vos tsu tun dermit.

00:07:54.317 --> 00:07:58.254
hob ikh un biz ikh hob mikh arumgekukt az zey nemen un esn dos oyf,

00:07:58.254 --> 00:07:59.880
hob ikh oykhet gevust.

00:08:00.004 --> 00:08:01.550
nor er hot mikh nisht oysgegebn.

00:08:01.590 --> 00:08:04.160
un eyn mol iz gekumen eyner

00:08:04.160 --> 00:08:06.765
vos iz geven dernokh vite-prezident.

00:08:07.885 --> 00:08:12.300
un er hot geze- un er hot mikh ongekukt un er hot bald derkent, a polyak.

00:08:08.830 --> 00:08:10.444
vi azoy hot er geheysn?

00:08:12.087 --> 00:08:13.785
vi azoy hot er geheysn?

00:08:13.909 --> 00:08:15.523
Kovalski dakht zikh.

00:08:16.795 --> 00:08:21.989
ikh hob ikh hob im gezen gikh oykhet dernokhn in UNK ven ikh hob gearbet,

00:08:21.989 --> 00:08:25.327
far zayn froy, hob i- zi hot zi hot zikh geneyt bay mir.

00:08:25.536 --> 00:08:28.182
hob ikh im shoyn mer nisht gezen.

00:08:28.182 --> 00:08:34.097
hob ikh, ikh hob im, m'hot mir gevizn, ven ikh bin aroys fun unter der erd, fun di goye,

00:08:34.097 --> 00:08:35.874
un gelegn azoy in a stok,

00:08:35.897 --> 00:08:38.304
hobn zey im gekent, di polyakn.

00:08:38.513 --> 00:08:40.380
er iz fun untergrunt.

00:08:40.655 --> 00:08:45.172
un dernokhn iz er gevezn vitse- vitse-prezident, unter Byerutn.

00:08:44.537 --> 00:08:47.028
un er hot oykh gevust ir zent a yid?

00:08:46.714 --> 00:08:48.407
er hot mir geg- ikh hob, ikh

00:08:48.407 --> 00:08:52.259
ikh veys nisht tsi er hot gevust loytn kukn, mir hot zikh dokh gedokhtn az yeder hot derkent.

00:08:52.333 --> 00:08:55.182
er hot mikh zikher derkent. er iz oykh gekumen zen

00:08:55.182 --> 00:09:01.693
vos es hert zikh. vayl s'dokh geven Varshever alding, opgelofn, vayl zey hobn gornisht gehat, alts iz dokh geven farbrent, polyakn.

00:09:05.918 --> 00:09:10.015
dernokhn iz zayn froy hob ikh oykh ge⟨UNK⟩. er hot gevoynt gor in Lodzh,

00:09:10.015 --> 00:09:13.002
nisht in Varshe, un zi iz gekumen,

00:09:13.002 --> 00:09:17.059
hot er mikh hobn zey mir gezogt az dos iz der Kovalskin,

00:09:17.059 --> 00:09:20.739
un dort hot zi oysbahaltn a yidish kind oykhet vos ikh hob gekent.

00:09:20.739 --> 00:09:25.599
vos er hot undz gegebn dem fabrik tsu arbetn fun gute zakhn. oyf Karmilitski.

00:09:25.599 --> 00:09:30.127
zi hot zikh nisht zi hot zikh nisht meyid geven. ikh hob ir derkent glaykh.

00:09:30.268 --> 00:09:31.612
nokh der milkhome.

00:09:32.378 --> 00:09:36.169
iz ir hot detsidirt ir geyt tsurik tsu fus keyn Varshe?

00:09:35.719 --> 00:09:38.143
s'nisht geve- s'geven azoy.

00:09:38.520 --> 00:09:44.234
s'geven ts- Bloyne iz geven, s'tsuzamen gevezn, ikh veys,

00:09:44.629 --> 00:09:48.369
nisht keyn draysik kilometer fun Varshe.

00:09:49.118 --> 00:09:52.397
f- Sokhotshov iz gevezn Lodzh,

00:09:52.397 --> 00:09:57.398
ikh gleyb az a draysik, ikh veys nisht vi azoy, m'geyt men az m'muz geyn geyt men.

00:10:01.774 --> 00:10:03.455
ikh bin dokh gevezn yung.

00:10:04.812 --> 00:10:11.792
vos a un ven ikh bin alt, ven ikh bin in aza MATZAV vi yetst, un afilek a besern, iz geven a reyd vegn iberlebn?

00:10:21.113 --> 00:10:27.227
ikh hob n- ikh hob nisht getrogn ikh hob nisht getrogn keyn tsu fil s- oyf di plet- s'nisht geven azoy shver.

00:10:27.227 --> 00:10:32.008
ikh hob mir gekent an eytse ge- ikh hob gehat gezunt. der ZUREK, di vos zi hot gemakht di zup,

00:10:32.200 --> 00:10:39.737
hob ikh es oysergeveyntlekh gut geven, s'iz gezunt geven tsu esn. s'epes geven geveykt broyt,

00:10:40.452 --> 00:10:44.411
un a zup oykhet epes aza, un dos hot gemakht zoyer,

00:10:44.434 --> 00:10:46.993
un s'iz un gegosn arayn milkh,

00:10:47.657 --> 00:10:49.423
un dos hobn zey gegesn.

00:10:49.564 --> 00:10:53.372
un ikh oykhet. UNK ikh hob gegesn tsu der zet bay ir.

00:10:53.867 --> 00:10:55.970
di por monatn vos ikh bin gevezn.

00:10:56.027 --> 00:10:59.345
un geven a shtub mit kinder, s'geven a por mamzeyrim oykhet.

00:10:59.807 --> 00:11:02.804
er hot gehat zeyer zeyer sheyne tsvey tekhter.

00:11:03.047 --> 00:11:05.116
un di tekhter hobn gehat mamzeyrim.

00:11:05.460 --> 00:11:10.145
eyne iz geven azoy sheyn, a a a MALKAT HAYOFI. di eltere.

00:11:11.468 --> 00:11:16.283
un nokh dem iz geven dem zun, hot zi gev- iz hot zi mir gegebn ontsugehern.

00:11:16.283 --> 00:11:20.962
ot derfar hob ikh ir dertseylt az mayn man iz a a ofitsir gevezn.

00:11:21.441 --> 00:11:26.143
un ikh veys er lebt zikher nisht, vayl m'hot gehert az zey hobn dershosn ofitsirn.

00:11:27.465 --> 00:11:30.761
iz un zog ikh, ikh hob ibergelozt

00:11:30.761 --> 00:11:36.618
dos kind, ikh bin gegangen do epes gevoyer, gebli- gegangen makhn a vizit, dervayl iz oysgebrokhn di oyfshtand.

00:11:36.618 --> 00:11:38.833
un yakh voyn gor iber der Vaysl,

00:11:41.775 --> 00:11:45.501
dertseylt a gantse zakh az ikh ken nisht khasene hobn mit im.

00:11:45.501 --> 00:11:50.021
un ikh volt y- tomer volt ikh gekent mikh oysredn farn galekh,

00:11:50.331 --> 00:11:51.543
ikh hob nisht gekent.

00:11:51.543 --> 00:11:57.834
ikh hob nisht far- far- gevust vos tsu zogn, volt ikh volt ikh dokh ba- gevorn farshit in gantsn.

00:12:01.941 --> 00:12:08.173
HAIKAR, mir haltn bay vos? bay geyn oyf oyfn veg tsu mitn kind, yo, shoyn nokh der bafrayung.

00:12:06.683 --> 00:12:07.200
yo.

00:12:08.173 --> 00:12:15.586
dos iz gevezn ikh gleyb in zibetsetn oder in akhtsetn yanuar finef un fertsik.

00:12:18.158 --> 00:12:21.881
vi iz, bay undz iz dos geven, s'nokh geven genug tsu,

00:12:22.005 --> 00:12:29.687
ober in der tsayt vos ikh bin gelegn untern frayen himl, vu di andere zayt hobn zenen keseyder ale geganen, take di vos

00:12:29.687 --> 00:12:34.389
di vos ikh bin mit ir gevezn unter der erd mitn man, iz oykh geganen keyn Prushkov.

00:12:34.498 --> 00:12:36.022
un zi hot ibergelebt.

00:12:38.037 --> 00:12:41.231
vayl nokh dem hot men zikh getrofn in komitet in Prage.

00:12:41.231 --> 00:12:45.658
nisht mit ir, nor mit im. hot er mir gezogt az zi lebt, zi iz lebn geblibn.

00:12:47.166 --> 00:12:50.015
un er hot gehat aza shlakhtn nomen,

00:12:50.015 --> 00:12:52.554
az az m'hot im gevolt nisht la-

00:12:52.554 --> 00:13:00.457
barn bar di vakhn flegt er ma- masern un nisht veln nemen adurkh nokh in di a- oyf der arisher zayt adurkh.

00:13:00.683 --> 00:13:05.216
farshidene zakhn. vi azoy hot er geheysn? ikh vel mikh dermanen. s'nisht vikhtik.

00:13:07.686 --> 00:13:09.632
un vu halt men yetst?

00:13:09.171 --> 00:13:11.949
iz ir ir geyt tsurik keyn Varshe.

00:13:09.632 --> 00:13:13.839
yo. yo ikh gey tsurik tsu keyn Varshe.

00:13:14.115 --> 00:13:18.120
un ikh geb a, ikh gey tsurik,

00:13:18.120 --> 00:13:20.943
un ikh vil visn vos iz gevorn fun di

00:13:21.068 --> 00:13:26.580
fun fun fun mayn shtub in Vlokhi, s'iz geven adurkhtsugeyn Varshe.

00:13:27.210 --> 00:13:32.115
un gey oyf dem veg, un ikh kum on.

00:13:32.273 --> 00:13:38.831
un ikh ze az di shtub iz do un zi di di tokhter fun Daytshland iz oykhet do, alts BESEDER.

00:13:39.681 --> 00:13:45.497
un ikh gey adurkh un ikh kum tsu tsu der Vaysl. der Vaysl iz gef- -efroyrn, un s'shteyt a vakh,

00:13:45.773 --> 00:13:51.285
militer un politsey, un ikh veys, private pevne ⟨didektivn⟩ oykhet,

00:13:51.321 --> 00:13:54.202
un lozn keynem nisht adurkh, un do shteyt a sakh mentshn.

00:13:54.202 --> 00:13:56.309
ale viln adurkh nokh Prage.

00:13:56.309 --> 00:14:01.004
ikh hob dokh ⟨gemuzt⟩ geyn nokh in vayter vi Prage. oyf Tekotshinski.

00:14:01.011 --> 00:14:05.595
s- s'hot dokh geheysn andersh, Targovek hot es geheysn.

00:14:06.934 --> 00:14:14.404
Targovek, Tekotshinski UNK z- zibn un tsvontsik Tekotshinski hot geheysn di gas.

00:14:12.823 --> 00:14:15.261
dortn iz er geven farshtekt?

00:14:14.486 --> 00:14:17.367
dort iz er gevezn bay Vrodlevskin.

00:14:18.072 --> 00:14:19.871
un ikh kum dort ahin,

00:14:20.788 --> 00:14:25.912
ikh kum ikh vil kumen tsu der Vaysl, ikh heyb mikh on betn, ikh kler zey oyf.

00:14:26.037 --> 00:14:27.415
ikh bin a yidishe,

00:14:27.572 --> 00:14:30.607
ikh hob ibergelozt a kind un ikh hob im ongerufn bay vemenen.

00:14:30.607 --> 00:14:33.274
vayl s'ken zayn zey hobn gekent az er iz geven vi a kontrolir,

00:14:33.274 --> 00:14:36.072
un a guter oyf di oyf dem tramvay.

00:14:36.111 --> 00:14:39.952
zog ikh, un ikh hob bay Vrodlevskin ibergelozt mayn kind,

00:14:40.026 --> 00:14:42.450
un ikh veys nisht tsi zi lebt tsi nisht.

00:14:42.540 --> 00:14:45.065
lozts mikh adurkh nokhn ⟨harts⟩!

00:14:45.173 --> 00:14:47.406
zest, zog ikh, ikh trog a por shikhlekh,

00:14:47.406 --> 00:14:50.145
un dos alts farn kind, tomer lebt es.

00:14:50.421 --> 00:14:53.784
lozts mikh dort azoy un oysnemlekh.

00:14:53.784 --> 00:14:56.068
oyf poylish zogt men DRODZE WYJATKU.

00:14:56.158 --> 00:14:59.535
un ikh hob zey on betn. a klal heybn zey zikh on baratn,

00:14:59.598 --> 00:15:02.848
di ale vos zey shteyen oyf vakh un lozn nisht adurkh nokh der Vaysl,

00:15:02.848 --> 00:15:10.108
beyde brikn. ⟨KERBEDZHA⟩, tsvey brikn geven adurkhtsugeyn. zenen gevorn tseshmetert, nisht geven.

00:15:10.435 --> 00:15:15.454
nor m'hot gemuzt vartn biz dos ayz vet avek, vet men kenen zikh adurkh shvimen,

00:15:15.454 --> 00:15:21.501
o- un ven m'vet farrekhtn di fabr- di di brikn oykhet oyf oyf di oyf Prage.

00:15:21.758 --> 00:15:23.965
alzo, ikh hob dokh gevolt shoyn adurkh,

00:15:23.965 --> 00:15:27.995
a klal, zey hobn mir adurkhgefirt un tsugefirt tsu N.K.V.D.

00:15:28.204 --> 00:15:32.383
un ikh hob mikh dort oykh dos zelbe gezogt dem emes, dafke dem emes,

00:15:32.490 --> 00:15:39.082
ikh bin a yidishe, ikh hob ibergelebt, ikh hob ibergelozt a kind bay Vroblevskin, oyf Tekotshinski zibn un tsvontsik,

00:15:39.207 --> 00:15:40.736
bay a gutn goy.

00:15:40.877 --> 00:15:43.588
un az er iz nishto, hob ikh nisht gevust.

00:15:44.218 --> 00:15:51.029
a klal, ikh kum ahin, ikh derken, ikh kum ahin, iz do epes rusishe ofitserkes voynen dortn,

00:15:51.222 --> 00:15:54.321
un ikh ze epes azan ayngeshrumpn nefesh,

00:15:54.512 --> 00:15:59.973
un zi iz do di goye. un un mit a shi- mit a tokhter hobn zey oykh gehat.

00:16:00.165 --> 00:16:02.719
un ikh ze az dos nefesh iz mayn kind.

00:16:02.719 --> 00:16:04.395
a koysh mit beyner.

00:16:06.240 --> 00:16:07.803
un zi derkent mikh.

00:16:08.248 --> 00:16:10.334
z- hot zi ongehoybn shrayen,

00:16:10.358 --> 00:16:13.333
oyf poylish, UNK.

00:16:13.333 --> 00:16:15.381
UNK.

00:16:15.825 --> 00:16:20.780
zi vil nisht zayn keyn yidishe. zi hot in ir azoy arayngegoret, un gevoygn hot zi tsvelef kilo.

00:16:21.040 --> 00:16:22.868
un vos dertseyln zey mir?

00:16:22.868 --> 00:16:28.577
az zint m'hot tsugenumen dem ale mener hot hobn zey mitgenumen azoy vi zey zenen opgetretn.

00:16:30.557 --> 00:16:35.314
di daytshn zenen opgetretn fun Prage, hobn zey mitgenumen aroys ale mener in lager arayn.

00:16:35.314 --> 00:16:38.388
azoy az zi iz gevezn a lange tsayt on im,

00:16:38.388 --> 00:16:40.999
un er iz geven a farantvortlekher mentsh,

00:16:40.999 --> 00:16:43.647
zi hot zikher nisht gekent shraybn, di tokhter efsher yo.

00:16:43.647 --> 00:16:46.221
ober er hot ir gelernt leyenen un shraybn,

00:16:46.221 --> 00:16:47.721
un zi hot im lib gehat,

00:16:47.721 --> 00:16:49.407
er hot oysgefirt di flikht,

00:16:49.454 --> 00:16:53.872
un a khuts dem hot vegn ir gevust der untergrunt oykhet.

00:16:54.047 --> 00:16:57.149
az bay Va- az bay Vroblevskin iz do a yidish kind.

00:16:57.149 --> 00:16:59.357
un ver dos kind hot men gekent.

00:17:03.058 --> 00:17:04.573
iz dokh mir biter.

00:17:04.573 --> 00:17:08.958
un do vil zogt zi UNK.

00:17:09.099 --> 00:17:13.492
un zi hot zikh mir PRZYZNAJEt, zi hot zikh mir gezogt, di goye,

00:17:13.492 --> 00:17:18.264
az s'iz zeyer shlekht geven, zi hot gekoyft afilek an ey far fertsik zlotes

00:17:18.264 --> 00:17:20.801
un zi vil nisht esn un zi ken nisht esn,

00:17:20.801 --> 00:17:24.172
un zi bet nor no- zi benkt nor nokhn nokhn DOD,

00:17:24.172 --> 00:17:27.453
nokhn nokhn feter, Vroblevski.

00:17:27.527 --> 00:17:35.329
un zi vil nisht esn un zi hot ir sh- zi iz shoyn geven barn barn galekh, barn KSIADZ,

00:17:35.329 --> 00:17:38.451
vayl bay keygn iber iz geven aza kleyne KOSCIOL

00:17:38.451 --> 00:17:39.925
oykh oyf di zelbe gas.

00:17:39.951 --> 00:17:43.784
un der g- galekh hot gemuzt visn ven zi iz aropgeganen zi iz a yidish kind.

00:17:43.784 --> 00:17:46.469
nor nisht ale zenen geven biter m'hot oysgegebn.

00:17:47.558 --> 00:17:54.251
un un z- m'da- zi vet zi vet zikh darfn bashventshyen vayl zi zi halt bay shtarbn.

00:17:56.113 --> 00:18:01.220
un in Prage dortn vu zi iz geven, shoyn a halb yor geven a yidishe komitet.

00:18:02.205 --> 00:18:05.240
un der yidishe komitet flegt tsunemen di kinder,

00:18:05.324 --> 00:18:09.287
oder er flegt gebn gelt az m'hot gevolt haltn, az s'geven vu tsu haltn.

00:18:09.287 --> 00:18:12.935
un zi di goye iz zi geven azan antisemit,

00:18:13.140 --> 00:18:18.821
az az zi hot nisht zi iz nisht geganen in yidishn komitet me- m- m- meldn az zi hot a yidish kind.

00:18:25.510 --> 00:18:27.141
az yo shoyn azoy,

00:18:28.075 --> 00:18:32.203
bin ikh gevoyer gevorn do- az s'do a yidishe komitet.

00:18:32.260 --> 00:18:36.575
a klal, ikh bin gegangen in yidishn komitet, der komitet iz shoyn geven oyfn tsveytn plats.

00:18:36.715 --> 00:18:41.569
bin ikh geven finef hundert un eyns koym faregistrirte yidishe.

00:18:41.794 --> 00:18:43.090
mener un froyen.

00:18:43.090 --> 00:18:47.891
finef un hundert un eyns iz geven mayn numer vu ikh hob mikh gemoldn in yidishn komitet.

00:18:47.891 --> 00:18:50.751
un ikh hob zey dertseylt, az ikh hob a kind,

00:18:50.751 --> 00:18:55.051
un in yidishn komitet hot gearbet eyner vos iz geganen mit mir tsuzamen

00:18:55.176 --> 00:18:58.714
iz geven oykhet a a a kamashn makher,

00:18:58.737 --> 00:19:03.568
un un fun eyn shtot ze'mir undz geven mi- mishpokhe fun mayn man oykhet,

00:19:03.568 --> 00:19:06.901
Zhelazer, er iz haynt, er lebt nokh efsher,

00:19:06.901 --> 00:19:09.497
vayl er iz gevorn a zhurnalist PITOM.

00:19:09.503 --> 00:19:16.587
a shlakhter mentsh, un er hot eyner gevust vegn dem Vrublevski, un er iz keyn eyn mol nisht geganen gevoyer vern, a,

00:19:16.587 --> 00:19:21.140
s'iz der vos ikh hob dir nokh nisht dertseylt, vos er hot mikh farbe- a ikh kum yetst dertsu.

00:19:22.041 --> 00:19:29.074
alzo er iz es iz gevezn un der vos hot gefirt dem Dzhoynt, dernokh iz er gevorn in eroplan derharget.

00:19:29.074 --> 00:19:33.636
der Dzh- der Dzhoynt in b- in in in in geto.

00:19:33.636 --> 00:19:37.673
geven gev- zey hobn gekokht un zupn un vos,

00:19:37.673 --> 00:19:41.710
un un Amerike hot arayngeshikt gelt iz oyf zayn adres gevezn,

00:19:41.781 --> 00:19:48.714
Dzh- Buzhik, er iz geharget gevorn, er iz geven. nokh dem geb ikh a kuk, az er iz oykhet do. Zhelazer.

00:19:48.923 --> 00:19:50.503
Noyekh Zhelazer.

00:19:50.728 --> 00:19:54.725
oy, er get mikh a derze, Rutkele!. oy!

00:19:54.725 --> 00:20:00.833
yakh hob ibergelebt do, zog ikh. zog ikh, far vozhe bistu nisht gegangen keyn eyn mol gevoyer vern vu dos kind iz?

00:20:00.833 --> 00:20:04.816
ts- vi azoy dos kind zet oys? du host dokh gekent, zog ikh, Rublevski!

00:20:04.816 --> 00:20:08.998
vos bistu nisht geganen eyn mol zikh vayzn, host ibergelebt in Grokhl?

00:20:09.173 --> 00:20:14.367
zogt er, ikh hob UNK, ikh ikh hob, zogt er, keseyder gehat, zog ikh, in zinen mitn kind,

00:20:14.367 --> 00:20:16.867
dos kind, zogt zi, dos kind, er hot gehat a yingele.

00:20:16.867 --> 00:20:18.423
un zi hot oysgezen azoy vi

00:20:18.423 --> 00:20:21.700
a rikhtike teymanke un er iz geven a blonder.

00:20:21.700 --> 00:20:28.843
nor er hot nisht gekent keyn gutn poylish. fun dest vegn hobn zey ibergelebt in Grokhov, dos heyst oykh oyf Shne- oykh UNK oyf di andere zayt Vaysl.

00:20:30.942 --> 00:20:34.465
un azoy vi er zogt er azoy zogt er tsu Guzhekn,

00:20:34.465 --> 00:20:36.878
z- zogt zi, vos iz mit gelt?

00:20:36.878 --> 00:20:43.147
zog ikh, ikh hob gelt, nor dos gelt iz do nishto do far vos tsu koyfn. s'geyt nisht do dos gelt fun yener zayt.

00:20:43.147 --> 00:20:45.988
do s'do ander gelt, Lubliner gelt.

00:20:46.163 --> 00:20:51.754
zogt er, yedere krigt tsvey toyznt zlotes. un far vos iz di goye nisht gekumen, zogt er, in komitet arayn?

00:20:51.754 --> 00:20:53.976
ikh bin dokh, zogt er, do fun der ershter minut on

00:20:53.976 --> 00:20:58.939
ikh hob dokh ibergelebt in Grokhov, zogt er, un ikh bin fun di ershte mitglider fun komitet.

00:20:59.055 --> 00:21:03.065
zogt er, iz zog ikh tsun im, zogt er, vu geystu nekhtikn?

00:21:03.274 --> 00:21:09.292
zogt er tsu Guzhekn, m'darf ir koydem gebn di tsvey hundert di tsvey toyznt zlotes.

00:21:09.720 --> 00:21:11.683
zogt er, vest geyn tsu mir,

00:21:11.683 --> 00:21:16.610
Dorke iz nishto, dos heyst di froy iz nishto, zi iz ergets in a git hot zi farnumen dortn bay Radzin.

00:21:16.610 --> 00:21:20.914
geven in ander plats vu s'oykhet di mishpokhe fun mayn man hot geshtamt,

00:21:20.914 --> 00:21:25.273
un vu di Kotsker khsidim zenen geven, vos ikh hob dir efsher dertseylt shoyn nekhtn.

00:21:26.427 --> 00:21:31.956
HAIKAR, iz iz, zogt er, "vest geyn tsu mir.

00:21:32.063 --> 00:21:38.236
vart unter, m'vet farmakhn di komitet, e'mir e'mir ves- vestu nekhtikn bay mir. bay mir iz do plats."

00:21:38.236 --> 00:21:40.623
ikh kum a- un m'kumt oyfn veg,

00:21:40.623 --> 00:21:46.080
koyft er shinke. shinke heyst vursht, poylishe.

00:21:47.272 --> 00:21:51.736
un a er koyft a vays broyt, un m'geyt aheym, a shtik vegs,

00:21:51.736 --> 00:21:54.200
oy- unter Prage nokh,

00:21:54.200 --> 00:22:00.845
un er un m'kumt ahin tsu im, er shlist oyf, a parter voynung, m'nisht geganen oyf keyn shtign,

00:22:01.003 --> 00:22:07.629
un ikh kum geb mikh a kuk arum, s'shtey- s'nor do eyn SAPA, eyn SAPA.

00:22:07.720 --> 00:22:12.067
un biz aroyf tsum sufit lign ayngeleygt SHETICHIM.

00:22:14.031 --> 00:22:22.633
az es do ligt a bret un ibern bret lign shoyn un un ikh ze nokh a shtub un in kekh un iberal iz SHETICHIM,

00:22:22.633 --> 00:22:30.039
ayngeleygte. persishe SHETICHIM fun goyim, azoy vi zey zenen geblibn, hobn zey opgerape- -evet.

00:22:31.041 --> 00:22:36.152
m'est op, yo, un er hot gekoyft di ke- di batus, mit di kabase mitn broyt,

00:22:36.152 --> 00:22:40.744
hot er bay mir genumen gelt fun di tsvey toyznt zlotes vos ikh hob gekrign fun komitet.

00:22:42.145 --> 00:22:44.147
shoyn, y- m'est op,

00:22:44.288 --> 00:22:49.327
ikh bin dokh geven z- oysergeveyntlekh mid, ikh hob dokh nisht gehat vu tsu zayn, un er iz avekgeganen,

00:22:51.105 --> 00:22:56.667
zogt zog ikh, vu vu velk ikh shlofn? zogt er, do oyf der SAPA. s'geven a breyte SAPA.

00:22:56.978 --> 00:23:01.393
un ikh ikh leyg mikh shlofn, ikh vil khapn a dos, er krikht arayn.

00:23:02.698 --> 00:23:06.961
zog ikh, "Noyekh! ikh hob nokh Godlen nisht farratn un du vest nisht zayn der ershter!"

00:23:08.824 --> 00:23:13.408
un geb mikh a shpring arop un geb mikh a tu on un zits azoy op biz in der fri.

00:23:16.013 --> 00:23:17.829
kumen biz in der fri,

00:23:17.920 --> 00:23:21.255
un ikh veys shoyn az dos kind lebt, az m'darf es opnemen,

00:23:21.447 --> 00:23:25.215
gey ikh in komitet arayn, alts tsu fus, s'nisht geven mit vos tsu forn.

00:23:25.215 --> 00:23:28.122
in Prage iz oykh geven alts hefker.

00:23:29.007 --> 00:23:32.375
kum in komitet arayn, un ikh shtey azoy.

00:23:32.466 --> 00:23:35.818
get a kum on der vos ikh bin gelegn mit im unter der erd,

00:23:35.908 --> 00:23:40.002
Ruznberg hot er geheysn, neyn, epes azoy endlekh, ikh gedenk nisht.

00:23:40.819 --> 00:23:42.838
ikh ken mikh di nisht nisht dermanen.

00:23:43.080 --> 00:23:47.714
un s'shteyt a redl mit ze- zelner vos geyen oyfn Berliner front,

00:23:47.805 --> 00:23:52.254
rusishe un poylishe, farshidene, a gants krentsl in komitet.

00:23:52.395 --> 00:23:57.536
un zey geyen zikh nemen tsu im shlogn, tsu dem vos ikh bin geven unter der erd mit der froy.

00:23:57.829 --> 00:24:03.931
vos iz? er hot oysgegebn mentshn, yinglekh bay der vakh. un m'hot zey dershosn.

00:24:04.427 --> 00:24:08.499
ikh hob nor badorfn zogn, ikh hob oykh gehat an avle, un mikh onrufn.

00:24:08.499 --> 00:24:10.372
zey voltn im gemakht toyt.

00:24:10.372 --> 00:24:12.347
ikh hob mikh gemakht nisht hern,

00:24:12.347 --> 00:24:16.162
nor er hot mir gegebn a zog dernokh, azoy vi zey hobn im ibergelozt

00:24:16.162 --> 00:24:21.088
lebn, im gornisht getun, zey hobn a bisl opgeharget un im do geshtupt, dortn gegebn a por boksn.

00:24:21.206 --> 00:24:24.536
nor ikh hob mikh in gantsn nisht ongerufn, ikh hob oykh gehat an avle.

00:24:24.829 --> 00:24:29.880
geyt er arop mit mir, zogt er, du veyst, zi iz oykh geblibn. dos heyst, di froy iz oykh geblibn lebn.

00:24:29.880 --> 00:24:33.361
zi iz, zogt er, avek keyn Prushkov, un zi zi hot epes gehat vemenen.

00:24:33.361 --> 00:24:35.084
nor s'kind, zogt er, lebt nisht.

00:24:35.084 --> 00:24:38.139
ale kinder fu- fun di Tshonkalezes hobn nisht gelebt.

00:24:38.139 --> 00:24:42.457
zenen oysgeshtorbn far hunger. poylishe kinder oykhet, kranke.

00:24:44.505 --> 00:24:53.341
a klal, un ikh zog ir, un ikh z- iz geb ikh get eyner a kum tsu mir tsu, an ofitsir vos geyt oykh oyfn front fun Berlin,

00:24:53.415 --> 00:24:55.569
un zogt, du bist Rutke?

00:24:56.267 --> 00:25:05.233
zog ikh, yo, ikh, un s'kind, zog ikh, iz geblibn lebn, nor s'iz, zog ikh, a a a skeletl, s'vegt tsvelef kilo in gantsn. s'halt shoyn bay shtarbn, zi hot es gevolt

00:25:05.233 --> 00:25:12.118
op- op- sh- opshmadn a- az er zol kenen s'zol kenen opshtarbn.

00:25:12.118 --> 00:25:15.447
un zi hot zikh nisht gevizn, zog ikh, in komitet arayn a gantse tsayt.

00:25:15.960 --> 00:25:18.513
zogt er azoy, ikh gey oyfn front,

00:25:18.513 --> 00:25:22.015
nor ikh kum yetst fun Mezritsh, dortn iz gevezn

00:25:22.015 --> 00:25:24.344
a MERKAZ fun oysarbetn barshtn.

00:25:24.344 --> 00:25:27.584
oyf poylish hot es geheysn MIEDZYRZ- MIEDZYRZEC,

00:25:27.584 --> 00:25:31.479
un oyf yidish hot men gezogt Mezritsh. dos iz geven a yidishe branzhe.

00:25:31.840 --> 00:25:34.283
dortn iz do hundert tsvontsik yidn,

00:25:34.283 --> 00:25:37.810
m'vet dikh, zogt er, dort iz do a a mishpokhe Sheymel,

00:25:37.810 --> 00:25:44.979
hobn zey farloyrn tsvey zin in poylishn oyfshtand, zey zenen geblibn lebn, un zey hobn fabrikn fun a ⟨gra⟩ mashine.

00:25:45.171 --> 00:25:48.483
un zey hobn gevoynt oyf der hoypt gas, oyf der Varshever gas.

00:25:48.483 --> 00:25:53.384
du vest dikh bay, hot er alding opgemoshlt, m'vet dikh, zogt er, tsukhapn, m'vet nisht visn vos tsu tun.

00:25:53.384 --> 00:25:55.310
un meyle vegn kind iz opgeredt,

00:25:55.310 --> 00:26:00.495
ikh ken, ikh volt mit dikh geforn, nor ikh muz mikh shoyn, zogt er, tsushteln, vayl undz gey'mir oyf Berlin.

00:26:01.017 --> 00:26:05.668
un zog ikh, ver bistu? zogt er, ikh hob gevoynt in dem ershtn, in a fatsyate.

00:26:05.691 --> 00:26:12.756
un mayn froy, zogt er, iz geven a Radzinerin, fun vanet mayn man shtamt. der ershter man.

00:26:12.795 --> 00:26:16.418
zogt er, un for oyf keyn Mezritsh.

00:26:16.609 --> 00:26:20.629
zog ikh, un vi azoy fort men? s'a komunikatsye? get zikh eyner a ruf on,

00:26:20.646 --> 00:26:25.905
ikh e- ikh darf forn keyn Mezritsh, ikh voyn, zogt er, bay bay di Sheymels.

00:26:26.076 --> 00:26:32.724
un ikh darf forn, zogt er, no, in a ofenem, a n- ikh hob, zogt er, a groyse

00:26:32.724 --> 00:26:36.279
a groysn vogn, un ofn, un s'iz a frost.

00:26:36.724 --> 00:26:38.923
zog ikh, s'nishto keyn eytse.

00:26:38.923 --> 00:26:43.808
zogt er, ruft zikh on nokh eyner, ikh voyn oykh, zogt er, bay di Sheymels.

00:26:43.808 --> 00:26:49.351
iz er shoyn gekumen mit britshesn ongetun, mit shtivelekh, elegant, er hot shoyn gehandlt mit valute.

00:26:49.351 --> 00:26:51.326
vayl er iz geven fun yener zayt Vaysl.

00:26:51.326 --> 00:26:53.846
zogt er, ikh voyn oykh bay di Sheymels,

00:26:54.021 --> 00:26:57.980
ikh vel dir, zogt dir, nemen dos kind, mit mir vet zi shoyn geyn.

00:26:59.185 --> 00:27:04.663
zibn a zeyger zay do, hob ikh opgeredt, zogt er, mit eynemen tsu forn in a

00:27:04.663 --> 00:27:09.557
SAMKHOT, in a groysn, in a last vogn, un zolst zayn.

00:27:09.883 --> 00:27:13.404
a klal, ikh hob dokh gezukht aza gelegnheyt,

00:27:15.672 --> 00:27:18.062
a klal, vi ikh nem dos kind,

00:27:18.895 --> 00:27:20.003
un

00:27:21.291 --> 00:27:27.528
un ikh, er kumt zibene, ikh derman mikh az zibene zol ikh zol er do zayn vi mir UNK hob mit im bashtelt barn komitet.

00:27:28.378 --> 00:27:31.848
get er kum on epes mit a pak un mit a kots,

00:27:31.939 --> 00:27:36.888
un do iz er do iz er shoyn, hot demolts geheysn azoy elegant, azelkhe britshesn mit shtivelekh,

00:27:36.902 --> 00:27:39.272
er hot fardint shoyn gelt, er hot gehandlt mit valute.

00:27:39.272 --> 00:27:40.981
valute veystu vos dos heyst?

00:27:40.073 --> 00:27:41.181
yo yo.

00:27:40.981 --> 00:27:45.551
ge- toyshn, gelter, dolarn, farshidene zakhn.

00:27:45.625 --> 00:27:50.057
vayl er iz shoyn geven a halb yor bafrayt, oyf yener zayt Vaysl.

00:27:51.767 --> 00:27:53.718
un er get mikh a fir tsu,

00:27:53.893 --> 00:27:57.366
un der forman vos ho-, der shofer heybt on redn,

00:27:57.366 --> 00:27:59.490
der shofer iz oykh geven in Treblinke.

00:28:00.002 --> 00:28:02.932
ibergelebt in Treblinke un geblibn lebn.

00:28:03.175 --> 00:28:05.295
dernokhn bin ikh gevoyer gevorn

00:28:05.408 --> 00:28:11.408
az er iz gevezn epes nisht in ordenung in Trebline, mayn man hot zikh dernokhn bakent mitn, er hot gevust,

00:28:11.408 --> 00:28:12.863
yakh hob im dertseylt vegn im,

00:28:12.863 --> 00:28:14.545
hot er gezogt, s'iz der vos hot gezogt

00:28:14.545 --> 00:28:16.567
m'darf nisht makhn keyn oyfshtand

00:28:16.567 --> 00:28:21.226
vayl s'nokh do a sakh arbet. dos heyst, s'nokh do fil toyte tsu tsu bagrobn.

00:28:22.648 --> 00:28:25.320
dos iz geven der der shofer,

00:28:25.320 --> 00:28:29.927
un er hot mir un tsuge- arayngefirt keyn Mezritsh,

00:28:29.927 --> 00:28:34.053
un ikh kum arayn, lekhtik, freylekh, ful mit mentshn.

00:28:34.053 --> 00:28:36.801
ale zenen dortn do. zenen gekumene,

00:28:37.701 --> 00:28:39.090
yo, ir kent vayter redn.

00:28:39.017 --> 00:28:42.574
z- ze- zenen ge- zenen gekumen tsurik

00:28:42.574 --> 00:28:47.280
fun fun Varshe hobn zey ibergelebt. tsvey zin zenen zey umgekumen,

00:28:47.320 --> 00:28:52.408
un fun di un di un un un zey zenen tsurikgeforn

00:28:52.459 --> 00:28:55.255
punkt in zelbn tog vos m'hot gezolt

00:28:55.255 --> 00:28:59.914
likvidirn zey di fabrikn, nemen un tsunemen zey far der regirung.

00:29:00.060 --> 00:29:04.908
hobn zey alts opgekrign, oyf der hoypt gas hobn zey gevoynt in di a- in a shtub,

00:29:04.908 --> 00:29:07.727
un un zey gebn arop a a f- a

00:29:07.727 --> 00:29:15.293
a a breyte a breytn f- SAPA tsu shlofn mitn kind in a bazunderer shtub,

00:29:15.552 --> 00:29:20.659
un zey visn nisht vos tsu tun, dort iz shoyn do a yidish meydl vos iz aropgenumen fun zibetsn yor.

00:29:20.698 --> 00:29:22.632
a yidishe fun di goyim.

00:29:22.808 --> 00:29:25.960
un ikh hob shoyn a shtub, m'veyst shoyn nisht vos tsu tun mit mir.

00:29:25.828 --> 00:29:30.449
undz ve'mir vayter derts- ir ikh vel aykh va- vayter fregn oyf di nekhste kasete.

00:29:25.960 --> 00:29:26.804
vosere,
